7 C. Unless otherwise provided by law, the Oklahoma Health Care
8 Authority shall provide coverage under the state Medicaid program to
9 children under the age of eighteen (18) years whose family incomes
10 do not exceed one hundred eighty-five percent (185%) of the federal
11 poverty level.
